transcript:
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Hello? Haan ji sir.
Executive: Ji sir, Tanuj baat karunga aapke saath. Maine meeting ka link bheja hua tha aapko subah bolte 3 baje karne join karne ke liye aapne.
Customer: Haan ji, chaliye abhi join kar lete hain. Aapka jo mail ID hai na, ye official mail ID hai aapki. Vikram.product@gmail.com.
Executive: Haan ji. Abhi karta hu.
Customer: Please main meeting mein.
Executive: Haan ji, haan ji.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer was sent a meeting link for 3:00 PM but has not joined yet.

- Customer asks if the executive's email ID, vikram.product@gmail.com, is the official one.



Resolution:

- Executive confirms the email ID.

- Executive will wait for the customer to join the meeting.



Next Steps: 

Issue not resolved. Customer will join the meeting.



Alert (If Any):

None
